    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/b947671cf7fa15426c887664a2269d4d.poster.avif?t=1729261843\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/b947671cf7fa15426c887664a2269d4d.webm?t=1729261843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/b947671cf7fa15426c887664a2269d4d.mp4?t=1729261843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Geomancers》是一款 PVP 卡牌回合制射击游戏，你和最多四位其他的朋友将扮演掌控强大元素魔法的巫师。你可以构建自己的法术牌组，并使用内建的关卡编辑器来随心所欲地塑造地形！用火球炸裂地形、召唤听从你吩咐的龙、窃取对手的法术，对作为巫师的你来说一切皆有可能！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/bb3c72379b722440970f2aaee23f836c.avif?t=1729261843\" width=609 height=132 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/39077a4030b3cf7594080b264fe1deea.poster.avif?t=1729261843\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/39077a4030b3cf7594080b264fe1deea.webm?t=1729261843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/39077a4030b3cf7594080b264fe1deea.mp4?t=1729261843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 释放你的破坏冲动，投掷火球、雪花飞轮、召唤天雷等等！<br></li><li> 操控你自己和其他巫师的魔法能量与法术，交换手牌、抽取额外的法术，或窃取他们施放的最后一个法术！<br></li><li> 用多种方式在世界中穿梭：你想要飞行、传送，还是干脆创造新的地面？</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/fc48816f6fe7cfc433405245ef653c6a.avif?t=1729261843\" width=609 height=138 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/2c3906586a8ca5f649062d8b9912281f.poster.avif?t=1729261843\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/2c3906586a8ca5f649062d8b9912281f.webm?t=1729261843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/2c3906586a8ca5f649062d8b9912281f.mp4?t=1729261843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 每个《Geomancers》的牌组都包含一张标志性法术，这张法术你每回合都能用。<br></li><li> 任何法术都可以成为标志性法术，解锁无限的战术潜力！<br></li><li> 然后用支持你战术的法术填充你的牌组！你会专注于获取额外的魔力和卡牌，还是直接向你的对手丢法术？</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/7fc5712b1dd2e6e80d8a1c00181d7a40.avif?t=1729261843\" width=609 height=162 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/3efccf7e0f3e8e196b6ec49fc217774f.poster.avif?t=1729261843\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/3efccf7e0f3e8e196b6ec49fc217774f.webm?t=1729261843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/3efccf7e0f3e8e196b6ec49fc217774f.mp4?t=1729261843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 挑战你的朋友进行巫师对战，无论是本地还是通过 Steam 远程游玩！<br></li><li> 可以进行自由混战或组队战，最后一名存活者获胜。<br></li><li> 通过各种可调整的限制来定制你的游戏体验。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/64099f364467766c9fd0da87b259aa91.avif?t=1729261843\" width=609 height=132 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/faa4b272ccbc3457e86f06a2840d93a2.poster.avif?t=1729261843\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/faa4b272ccbc3457e86f06a2840d93a2.webm?t=1729261843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127910/extras/faa4b272ccbc3457e86f06a2840d93a2.mp4?t=1729261843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 选择多种地形类型来给游戏增添个人风格，包括土壤、草地、石头、冰雪、淤泥等等！<br></li><li> 根据不同的季节主题设置气氛，如秋季和冬季。<br></li><li> 导入和导出其他玩家制作的关卡！</li></ul>",
